summary: Change the skyrim graphics to cartoon like(e.g.prince of persia 2008)
descriptionHtml:
Did you ever imagined that if skyrim were made in cartoonish  graphics. You don\'t have think it anymore, because this mod changes the skyrim visuals to the one like \"prince of persia\" or \"borderlands\". This mod combines \"ENB series\" and \"FXAA injector\".

Installation:
 Just put all files in skyrim folder. Backup your ENB files if you are using them
author: FAIZY56
